text: Zdeněk Dohnal (born 11 August 1948) is a Czech former cyclist. He competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics and 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Czechoslovakia Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:People from Znojmo
